<!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="{{ locale }}" dir="{{ direction }}" class="{{ checkout_html_classes }}">
      <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, height=device-height, minimum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
        <meta name="referrer" content="origin">
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{ 'favicon.png' | asset_url }}" type="image/png" />
        <style type="text/css">
          @font-face {
            font-family: 'Montserrat';
            src: url({{'Montserrat-Regular.eot'| asset_url }});
            src: url({{'Montserrat-Regular.eot'| asset_url }}) format('embedded-opentype'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Regular.woff2'| asset_url}}) format('woff2'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Regular.woff'| asset_url}}) format('woff'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Regular.ttf'| asset_url}}) format('truetype'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Regular.svg'| asset_url }}) format('svg');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
          }
          @font-face {
            font-family: 'Montserrat';
            src: url({{'Montserrat-Medium.eot'| file_url }});
            src: url({{'Montserrat-Medium.eot?#iefix'| file_url }}) format('embedded-opentype'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Medium.woff2'| file_url}}) format('woff2'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Medium.woff'| file_url}}) format('woff'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Medium.ttf'| file_url}}) format('truetype'),
            url({{'Montserrat-Medium.svg'| file_url }}) format('svg');
            font-weight: 500;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
          }
          @font-face {
            font-family: 'Open Sans';
            src: url({{'OpenSans-Regular.eot' | file_url }});
            src: url({{'OpenSans-Regular.eot' | file_url }}) format('embedded-opentype'),
                url({{'OpenSans-Regular.woff' | file_url }}) format('woff'),
                url({{'OpenSans-Regular.woff2' | file_url }}) format('woff2'),
                url({{'OpenSans-Regular.ttf' | file_url }}) format('truetype'),
                url({{'OpenSans-Regular.svg' | file_url }}) format('svg');
            font-weight: normal;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
          }
          @font-face {
            font-family: 'Open Sans';
            src: url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.eot' | file_url }});
            src: url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.eot' | file_url }}) format('embedded-opentype'),
                url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.woff' | file_url }}) format('woff'),
                url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.woff2' | file_url }}) format('woff2'),
                url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.ttf' | file_url }}) format('truetype'),
                url({{'OpenSans-SemiBold.svg' | file_url }}) format('svg');
            font-weight: bold;
            font-style: normal;
            font-display: swap;
          }
          .btn {
            border-radius: 7px;
          }
          .btn__content {
            color:  #fff;
            line-height:  1.11;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
          }
          .alt-payment-list-container, .alternative-payment-separator{display:none !important;}
          .checkout-header{
            top: 0px;
            position: sticky;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 500;
          }
          .checkout-header .header__top-container{
              position: relative;
              background-color: #1B3281;
              z-index: 20;
              height: 2.675rem;
          }      
          .checkout-header .header__top{
              display: -webkit-box;
              display: -webkit-flex;
              display: -moz-box;
              display: -moz-flex;
              display: -ms-flexbox;
              display: flex;
              -webkit-box-align: center;
              -ms-flex-align: center;
              -moz-box-align: center;
              -ms-grid-row-align: center;
              -webkit-align-items: center;
              -moz-align-items: center;
              align-items: center;
              -webkit-box-pack: center;
              -ms-flex-pack: center;
              -moz-box-pack: center;
              -webkit-justify-content: center;
              -moz-justify-content: center;
              justify-content: center;
              height: 2.675rem;
              font-family: "Montserrat",Arial,sans-serif;
              font-size: 0.625rem;
              font-weight: 700;
              color: #fff;
              line-height: 35px;
          }
          @media only screen and (min-width: 992px){
              .checkout-header .header__top {
                  padding: 0 20px;
                  margin: 0 auto;
                  height: 40px;
                  max-width: 1360px;
                  line-height: 40px;
                  font-size: 18px;
              }
          }
          .checkout-header .header__promo{
              text-align: center;
              white-space: nowrap;
              text-overflow: ellipsis;
              overflow: hidden;
          }
          .checkout-header .header__promo a{
              color: #fff;
              text-decoration:underline;
          }
          @media (max-width: 767px){
              .hidden-xs {
                  display: none!important;
              }
          }
          .btn--subdued .btn__content {color:#000 !important;}
        </style>

        <title>{{ page_title }}</title>
    
        {{ content_for_header }}
    
        {{ checkout_stylesheets }}
        {{ checkout_scripts }}

        {{ settings.script_checkout_js }}
      </head>
      <body>
        <div class="overlay"></div>  
        {{ skip_to_content_link }}
    
        <header class="banner" data-header role="banner">
          <div class="wrap">
            {{ content_for_logo }}
          </div>
        </header>
    
        {{ order_summary_toggle }}
        <div class="content" data-content>
          {%- unless settings.promotion_text == blank -%}
            <header class="checkout-header">
              <div class="header__top-container">
                <div class="header__top">
                  <div class="header__promo">
                    {{ settings.promotion_text }}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          </header>
          {%- endunless -%}
          <div class="wrap">
            <div class="main">
              <header class="main__header">
                {{ content_for_logo }}
                {{ breadcrumb }}
                {{ alternative_payment_methods }}
              </header>
              <main class="main__content">
                {{ content_for_layout }}
              </main>
              <footer class="main__footer">
                {{ content_for_footer }}
              </footer>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar" role="complementary">
              <div class="sidebar__header">
                {{ content_for_logo }}
              </div>
              <div class="sidebar__content">
                {{ content_for_order_summary }}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="country_poup" style="display:none;">  
      <header>
        <h2>{{ settings.country_popup_title }}</h2>
        <svg class="icon-svg icon-svg--color-adaptive-lighter icon-svg--size-16 icon-svg--block icon-svg--center" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"> <use xlink:href="#question"></use> </svg>
      </header>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="country_cnt">
      {{ settings.country_popup }}
    </div>
      <div class="country_cls">
        <a href="JavaScript:void(0)">Close</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="shipping_poup" style="display:none;">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="country_cnt">
          <p>If you havenâ€™t done so already, once you have placed your order please <a target="_blank" href="https://mydhl.express.dhl/ca/en/forms/clearance-for-individuals.html">click here</a> to set up your Power of Attorney.</p>
          <p>This will allow DHL to move your order through Customs. You will only need to do this once.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="shipping_cls">
          <a href="JavaScript:void(0)">Close</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="korea_poup" style="display:none;">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="country_cnt">
          <p style="font-weight: 700;">We are unable to ship Organ Ultra and Pure NZ Sheep Placenta to South Korea.</p>
          <p style="font-weight: 700;">Please remove these from your cart to complete your purchase.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="korea_cls">
          <a href="JavaScript:void(0)" onclick="return myClosePopup();">Close</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      {{ tracking_code }}

      {% include 'checkout.additional_scripts' %}
      {% include 'checkout.additional_styles' %}
      </body>
    </html>
    